            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="119808942">
            下面隆重推出我为了更好分享旅游经验的而发的榜单！！！
        </p>
            <div data-seq="119809863" data-index="4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t8"><span class="_j_anchor">Alice梦游蔷薇榜</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="119809913">
            景点风光：6颗心<br />
适合旅游季节：一年四季<br />
适合人群：任何年龄段（随时休息，有缆车，可休闲锻炼，可了解历史知识）<br />
交通情况：旺季一大堵点，淡季交通不错，有公交车，不同地铁，北五环外，公园东门有停车场，也有不正规民房私有停车位。停车费嘛，一次性不限时10-20元（现价）。<br />
配套设施：公园内有卖饮食和纪念品，随地做，卫生间没去过没发言权；公园外餐厅很多<br />
人均消费：5元以上不封顶<br />
推荐指数：6心推荐！（推荐指数共7心）<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_119808963" data-seq="119808964" data-pid="119808963" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="12616368">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_5433780/119808963.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/0E/CB/wKgBs1boyxqAEVaTAAVbACFKUag88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/0E/CB/wKgBs1boyxqAEVaTAAVbACFKUag88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="119808963" alt="" />
        </a>
